data.description: Welcome to this highly coveted home in “The Timbers" of Dalraida. This conveniently located 3BD/2BA, 1626 square foot home offers TRULY PREMIER LIVING AT ITS BEST!  Enter into a spacious greatroom with fireplace and exquisite wood flooring and a formal dining room that can be used as a flex space. The primary suite is liberally-sized and offers a spa-like, relaxing ensuite bath that has double vanity sinks, a garden tub, separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. The separate guest quarters give your guests comfortable-sized rooms with a well appointed guest bathroom. The kitchen exudes a level of craftsmanship rarely seen in a home this size and is complete with granite countertops, tile backsplash, work island, tile flooring, with stainless steel appliances.  The breakfast nook provides an array of natural light and opens to the relaxing covered patio for enjoyment of the relaxing privately fenced exterior living space, great backyard with space for gardening, lush grass, irrigation system with plenty of storage space with covered parking. Enjoy the quality updates of this exquisite home all for UNDER 200k! Schedule a private tour TODAY!
